org.cryptacular.bean

Class BufferedBlockCipherBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cryptacular.bean.AbstractCipherBean
      • org.cryptacular.bean.AbstractBlockCipherBean
        • org.cryptacular.bean.BufferedBlockCipherBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CipherBean

    public class BufferedBlockCipherBean
extends AbstractBlockCipherBean
    Cipher bean that performs symmetric encryption/decryption using a standard block cipher in a standard mode (e.g. CBC, OFB) with padding to support processing inputs of arbitrary length.
    Author:
    Middleware Services
